## Limitations
The report is based on available online resources and may not cover all aspects of teen health initiatives in schools. Additionally, the findings are limited to the context of the sources reviewed and may not reflect the latest developments in school health programs. Further research and data collection from diverse educational settings would provide a more comprehensive understanding of the topic.